name: PUSH UPS
instructions: To start the workout, elbows must be locked up before starting the work out, the chest must touch the ground in every repetition.

name: SIT UPS
instructions: To start the workout, feet must be in butterfly position, hands touching the ground on the back of your head, repetition counts when both hands touch the floor in front of the feet.

name: AIR SQUATS
instructions: To start the workout, body must be at full extension (knees and hips straight), repetition counts when hips break parallel with the knees and go to full extension with the bar on the back.

name: STRICT PULL UPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the bar with both arms at full extension, repetition counts when the chin passes over the bar.

name: BUTTERFLY PULL UPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the bar with both arms at full extension, repetition counts when the chin passes over the bar.

name: CHEST TO BAR PULL UPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the bar with both arms at full extension, repetition counts when the chest touches the bar.

name: BAR MUSCLE UPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the bar with both arms at full extension, repetition counts when player finishes the dip over the bar.

name: RING MUSCLE UPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the rings with both arms at full extension, repetition counts when player finishes the dip over the rings.

name: TOES TO BAR
instructions: To start the workout, player must be hanging on the bar with both arms at full extension, the repetition counts when both feet touch the bar.

name: BENCH PRESS
instructions: To start the workout, player must have both arms fully extended grabbing with the bar, repetition counts when the bar touches the chest and go up to full extension of the arms.

name: BACK SQUAT
instructions: To start the workout, body must be at full extension (knees and hips straight), repetition counts when hips break parallel with the knees and go to full extension with the bar on the back.

name: DEAD LIFT
instructions: To start the workout, player must grab the bar with both hands outside the knees and pull the bar up, repetition counts when player reaches full extension of the body.

name: SQUAT SNATCH
instructions: To start the workout, player must grab the bar with both hands outside the knees, pull to overhead and catch in the bottom of the squat, repetition counts when player fully extends the body with the bar overhead.

name: CLEAN AND JERK
instructions: To start the workout, player must grab the bar with both hands outside the knees, pull to front rack position and push the bar overhead, repetition counts when player fully extends the body with the bar overhead.

name: BOX JUMPS
instructions: To start the workout, player must stand with both feet on the ground and jump on top of the box, repetition counts when player fully extends the body on top of the box.

name: KETTLEBELL SWINGS
instructions: To start the workout, player must hold the kettlebell with both hands and pull to overhead position, repetition counts when player fully extends the body with the kettlebell overhead.
